desc:
You transform into an amoebic form composed of highly acidic and poisonous alchemical jelly. While in this form:
* you are immune to ácido and dano de veneno and to the envenenado and atordoado conditions;
* you have resistance to não mágico fogo, perfurante, and dano cortante;
* you can’t speak, cast spells, use items or weapons, or manipulate objects;
* your gear melds into your body and reappears when the spell ends;
* you don't need to breathe;
* your Deslocamento is 20 pés;
* your size doesn’t change, but you can move through and between obstructions as if you were two size categories smaller; and
* you gain the following action: **ataque corpo a corpo com arma:** spellcasting ability modifier + proficiência bonus para acertar, range 5 ft., um alvo; **Hit:** 4d6 ácido or dano de veneno (your choice), and the alvo deve fazer a successful teste de resistência de Constituição ou ficar envenenado until the start of your next turn.
